{"tid":764810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰自助海鮮老闆哭訴：中國遊客  “不要臉”","createTime":"2018-08-02T09:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T19:05:56.000Z","uid":1221,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"18ca0b990a2f8afb957bbd0bf7ff1700ddcc9b99","tid":764810,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2018/0801/20180801104317971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2018%2F0801%2F20180801104317971.jpg&h=726bb189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這幾年來到泰國去旅遊的人越來越多了，大家都知道泰國這個地方盛產海鮮，所以海鮮的價格十分便宜。只需要花上不多的錢，就可以吃上一頓豐富的海鮮大餐，不過前段時間卻有一家泰國自助海鮮店的老闆哭訴中國遊客 &ldquo;不要臉&rdquo;，這究竟是怎麼一回事呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2018/0801/20180801104318293.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2018%2F0801%2F20180801104318293.jpg&h=93946257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想必就算是沒有出過國的人在國內也是見過自助餐的吧，自助餐這種吃飯的形式就是你花不太多的錢就可以吃遍所有的食物，可以說是一種非常划算的消費形式了。不過自助餐廳也有規定，那就是你拿的食物是多少，你就必須吃完，如果吃不完的話，就會按重量來讓你多付錢。這其實也是理所應當的，因為不能浪費嘛。<br />\n<br />\n但是去了泰國旅遊的這群人，彷彿忘了這麼一個規定，因為自己肚子小眼睛大，拿了很多的食物卻吃不完，於是就自作聰明的將這些海鮮故意烤焦。烤焦之後的食物自然是不能吃的啦，而且老闆也不能說什麼，總不能讓人家把烤焦的食物給吃下去吧。於是很多吃不完東西的遊客都紛紛效仿這種做法，實在讓人覺得有些&ldquo;不要臉&rdquo;了。很多網友也評論這群人真的是太讓人覺得沒素質了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2018/0801/20180801104318675.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2018%2F0801%2F20180801104318675.jpg&h=94d21038&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89e557578dbcba769f00d5d00f18cc5d37bcfef4","tid":764810,"uid":63909,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:14:56.000Z","msg":"中國人要臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有著數嘅老豆都點喇"},{"pid":"4ce4809694ae6b2c6a0519cdc6c8136a75eb5061","tid":764810,"uid":141869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:15:25.000Z","msg":"又真係仆街得來吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752a29a1301422d4411129221a8b137a18786a4e","tid":764810,"uid":44504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"又係大陸狗"},{"pid":"73c20a6b2cfc46027f6a94df08e81a1478e5fb16","tid":764810,"uid":156005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:19:01.000Z","msg":"照呼得大陸人預左係咁仆街<br />\n任飲又袋走，任食食唔落又照拎"},{"pid":"9ae95fab365f4ae6f3c5ecac518a798f64de82fd","tid":764810,"uid":74262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:22:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4908ce0ba3b2606ec3f7f3fbd225c30f6260eb03","tid":764810,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/172242_bc12362444b434d73fe4f42521eeff23.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F172242_bc12362444b434d73fe4f42521eeff23.gif&h=d9027699&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55603b87c522b240fc79a935dd0f0e3c593dea85","tid":764810,"uid":25673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"拆左個烤爐佢咁未屈唔到機囉"},{"pid":"38e3e135d411ce303e2a7059bed28fc31c607094","tid":764810,"uid":67500,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:45:17.000Z","msg":"唔好做中國人生意，俾D骨氣"},{"pid":"1ff71da32eab0f940f3519eb594c59673ae0e745","tid":764810,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb788c1e99a64505ad896636d15a2b6dcfb0bc1","tid":764810,"uid":72735,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"轉香港放題style<br />\n餐廳煮比客食<br />\n寫十份黎兩份<br />\n食完先上下轉<br />\nsolved"},{"pid":"af23f701ee53b5d5b542e617a083bcbdb0b8f9f0","tid"